{"tid":373052,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"你地會買咩狗糧俾狗仔食？","createTime":"2017-08-24T17:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T18:11:34.000Z","uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbb3580cea585eabead292cafec235d489de9e6","tid":373052,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:27:05.000Z","msg":"市面上好多出名嘅狗糧都俾人話有唔好嘅成分<br />\n今日買包pronature holistic 狗糧<br />\n上網一check 就會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人發現Pronature含有Menadione（甲萘醌）維生素K3有害物質，吃了會嚴重減弱免疫系統、導致皮膚和黏膜極度敏感。許多歐洲國家已禁止了 Menadione（甲萘醌）用於人的食物裡，基於它的副作用, 可導致永久損傷和死亡 。（其他含維生素K3的狗糧品牌包括 1st choice, Natural Life及 Fromm等） <br />\n想自己隻狗仔食得健康啲都咁難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴絲有咩健康嘅狗糧推介下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9d84a0a638ba09fecdc178d13f851ee49009f7","tid":373052,"uid":52050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:38:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.petelements.hk/image/cache/data/Canidae%20new%20photos/CANIDAE%20卡比%20無穀物幼犬配方狗糧%20-%20鮮雞肉配鯡魚-550x650.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.petelements.hk%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fdata%2FCanidae%2520new%2520photos%2FCANIDAE%2520%E5%8D%A1%E6%AF%94%2520%E7%84%A1%E7%A9%80%E7%89%A9%E5%B9%BC%E7%8A%AC%E9%85%8D%E6%96%B9%E7%8B%97%E7%B3%A7%2520-%2520%E9%AE%AE%E9%9B%9E%E8%82%89%E9%85%8D%E9%AF%A1%E9%AD%9A-550x650.png&d=Npv5wDLWnBRp1i3akIOPzjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e9384908\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.petelements.hk/image/cache/data/Canidae%20new%20photos/CANIDAE%20卡比%20無穀物幼犬配方狗糧%20-%20鮮雞肉配鯡魚-550x650.png</a><br />\n<br />\n唐狗仔 6個月大 佢食左三個月 d毛好有光澤 <br />\n之前比過taste of the wild 但全犬糧好似比puppy食唔係咁好 所以轉左食canidae"},{"pid":"b2a09b49d29cacb35a8be1724c39210e675da397","tid":373052,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.petelements.hk/image/cache/data/Canidae%20new%20photos/CANIDAE%20卡比%20無穀物幼犬配方狗糧%20-%20鮮雞肉配鯡魚-550x650.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.petelements.hk%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fdata%2FCanidae%2520new%2520photos%2FCANIDAE%2520%E5%8D%A1%E6%AF%94%2520%E7%84%A1%E7%A9%80%E7%89%A9%E5%B9%BC%E7%8A%AC%E9%85%8D%E6%96%B9%E7%8B%97%E7%B3%A7%2520-%2520%E9%AE%AE%E9%9B%9E%E8%82%89%E9%85%8D%E9%AF%A1%E9%AD%9A-550x650.png&d=Npv5wDLWnBRp1i3akIOPzjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=e9384908\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.petelements.hk/image/cache/data/Canidae%20new%20photos/CANIDAE%20卡比%20無穀物幼犬配方狗糧%20-%20鮮雞肉配鯡魚-550x650.png</a><br />\n<br />\n唐狗仔 6個月大 佢食左三個月 d毛好有光澤 <br />\n之前比過taste of the wild 但全犬糧好似比puppy食唔係咁好 所以轉左食canidae</blockquote><br />\n我個隻係積羅素 2歲半 而隻好似唔係好啱<br />\n但唔該你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1abab6bf28a8834df9f7410e9abd4d01c8022222","tid":373052,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:05:10.000Z","msg":"就兩歲開始轉食生肉糧"},{"pid":"d0aa07f5827a402400884ab87ae990a0b5de8848","tid":373052,"uid":14093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T18:11:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就兩歲開始轉食生肉糧</blockquote><br />\n有咩牌子介紹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}